                    <span>...then this book's for you. Geared toward directors, producers, editors, and anyone (including writers), the book talks about story and structure as basic to any kind of film. Also has interviews with experts on archival use, historical films, cinema verite and more. Useful and straightforward.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">ESSENTIAL!</div>
